{"tid":999774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求兒子優先求醫　大媽推跌廣華姑娘被捕","createTime":"2019-01-29T03:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T03:37:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a00316b792732e717a116a37f2c09518e66f1876","tid":999774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190129/large/1548732393_0384.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F1548732393_0384.jpg&h=0cafd1db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名持身份證帶內地口音的41歲女子，帶同年約7歲、疑喉嚨痛的兒子，到旺角廣華醫院急症室求醫，經分流後並不屬於緊急，據知有人多次擅自進入診療室，並大吵大鬧，要求先讓其兒子看醫生。<br />\n<br />\n至凌晨約3時半，她再次吵鬧時，推跌上前勸阻的45歲姓羅姑娘，羅姑娘墮地後手部受傷，於是通知駐院警員，警員以涉嫌襲擊拘捕該女子，並召警車將她帶走。"},{"pid":"2a01a0c9fbb39ecd334c8eed88c88d9fc6367d45","tid":999774,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190129/59197097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197097&d=1PcJbJtZkx%2BFkqhBF7gQcwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=0e110d5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197097&h=075672a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190129/59197097</a>"},{"pid":"5072a411372e644bd8ed471af569b520ced6ced9","tid":999774,"uid":81190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"Pollutant <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb75ea9ae8624dca31e647fe49617ac1ea838ab","tid":999774,"uid":218196,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"快D搵明星打氣, 跌低同佢講: 加油快D 自己爬返起身睇症"},{"pid":"3e026539efc4dcd30a62